00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:09,880
and a quart of macaroni
salad shoved up your...

335
00:16:10,260 --> 00:16:11,080
What?

336
00:16:12,060 --> 00:16:13,410
t her self-hushing emblem.

337
00:16:13,730 --> 00:16:14,820
She knows something.

