00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:47,170
Well,that is the kind
of emotionally detached

375
00:17:47,170 --> 00:17:49,170
scientific analysis
we value around here.

376
00:17:49,170 --> 00:17:50,790
I'll be sure to pass
that on to the governor.

